ToDo Application Prerequisites:
===================================
Technologies: 
	Angular JS, 
	HTML5,
	Bootstrap,
	SpringBoot, 
	IBM Informix DB, 
	Hibernate 5
	

Database Queries:
===================
set autocommit=1;
create database localdatabase in dbs0 with log;
commit;

CREATE TABLE todo_items(
	id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
	name VARCHAR(50) not null,
	description varchar(200), 
	todo_date date, 
	status varchar(20) not null
);


DB Connection Details:
=======================
URL: jdbc:informix-sqli://localhost:9998/localdatabase:INFORMIXSERVER=nallamachu
UN: informix
